revision.text:
{{Documentation subpage}}
<!-- PLEASE ADD CATEGORIES WHERE INDICATED AT THE BOTTOM OF THIS PAGE -->
{{Uses Wikidata|P402}}
=== Usage ===
<syntaxhighlight lang="wikitext">
{{OSM relation|OpenStreetMap relation number}}
</syntaxhighlight>
This template creates an inline link to an OpenStreetMap relation.

; Full syntax
<syntaxhighlight lang="wikitext">
{{OSM relation|OpenStreetMap relation number|Link text}}
</syntaxhighlight>
The first value from Wikidata is used if the first parameter is empty.

* Normal
<syntaxhighlight lang="wikitext">{{OSM relation|21032}}</syntaxhighlight>
{{OSM relation|21032}}

* Text override
<syntaxhighlight lang="wikitext">{{OSM relation|21032|Bundesautobahn 2}}</syntaxhighlight>
{{OSM relation|21032|Bundesautobahn 2}}

; Using {{para|plain|yes}}
* Normal
<syntaxhighlight lang="wikitext">{{OSM relation|21032|plain=yes}}</syntaxhighlight>
{{OSM relation|21032|plain=yes}}

* Text override
<syntaxhighlight lang="wikitext">{{OSM relation|21032|Bundesautobahn 2|plain=yes}}</syntaxhighlight>
{{OSM relation|21032|Bundesautobahn 2|plain=yes}}

; Using {{para|link|no}}
<syntaxhighlight lang="wikitext">{{OSM relation|21032|Bundesautobahn 2|link=no}}</syntaxhighlight>
{{OSM relation|21032|Bundesautobahn 2|link=no}}

===See also===
* [[Template:Osm]]

<includeonly>{{Sandbox other|
| <!-- CATEGORIES BELOW THIS LINE, PLEASE: -->
[[Category:External link templates to linked data sites with reciprocal links]]
[[Category:OpenStreetMap templates]]

}}</includeonly>

